--------------------------------------------------------------

   JIMI HENDRIX - WAIT UNTIL TOMORROW. From AXIS: BOLD AS LOVE
                  album. Released on 1st December 1967.

--------------------------------------------------------------

    Tabbed by:PJVillanueva




